{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_08_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 莉央への密着インタビュー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2088542064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\n莉央さん、決まりました！　決まりましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff…\nRio-san‚ it’s decided! It’s decided!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、何をそんなに興奮してるの？\n慌てるなんて、貴方らしくないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what are you so excited about?\nYou’re not usually flustered like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2280274749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まずは汗を拭きなさい。レッスン中の私より汗だくよ\nもう……用事なら、電話かメッセで良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wipe your sweat first. You're sweating more than me during practice.\nGeez… You could've just called or texted me if you had something to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6946941416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません\n重大なことですし、直接伝えたいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry.\nI wanted to tell you in person because it's important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666665752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。で、どうしたの？\nその様子だと、大きな仕事でも決まったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright. So‚ what’s up?\nJudging by your reaction‚ did you land a big job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9884819706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりライブ？　それともCMかしら\n地上波のCMなら、確かに大きな仕事よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it a live performance after all? Or a commercial?\nIf it’s a commercial on a terrestrial channel‚ it’s definitely a big deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8551486373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "年末の例の番組に、LizNoir出演確定です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s confirmed that LizNoir will appear on that year-end program!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7551485101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん、そうなの。私達が年末のあの番組に\n出演が決まった――って、え！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ is that so. We’ve been confirmed\nto appear on that year-end program… Huh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8208239913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "年末のあの番組って……アレよね？\n大晦日の夜の、国民的歌番組……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That year-end program… you mean that one‚ right?\nThat national music program on New Year's Eve…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8402280848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、うちの事務所では麻奈以来の快挙です！\nおめでとうございます。さすがLiznoirですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ it’s the first time for our agency since Mana!\nCongratulations. As expected of LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5666665752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがと……えっ、待って待って\nまだ頭が状況に追いついてないの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-thank you… Uh‚ wait‚ wait.\nMy mind hasn’t caught up with the situation yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1481874507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どの曲を歌えばいいのかしら……\nみんなと相談しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what song should we sing…?\nI need to discuss it with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9481874507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……って、誰もいないじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ no‚ there’s no one here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もう、どうしてこんな日に限って\n全体練習の時間が遅いのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ why does the\ngroup practice time have to be so late?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5587132934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、落ち着いて下さい\n他のメンバーには俺からちゃんと伝えますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ calm down.\nI’ll be sure to tell the other members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5000014344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　それじゃ頼むわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is that so? Then I’ll leave it to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4333815932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺がまず最初に莉央さんにだけ伝えたのは\n折り入ってお願いがあるからなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason why I told Rio-san first\nis because I have a favor to ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7333347677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "お願い……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A favor…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0451049526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9284387946
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9284387946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "私を撮影したい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to film me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9784387946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。練習風景や休憩しているところを撮影しつつ\nリーダーの莉央さんにインタビューさせてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I want to film Rio-san while you’re practicing and taking breaks‚\nand interview you‚ the leader.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2333347677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ドキュメンタリー風に構成して、事前特番で使うそうで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re going to edit it into a documentary and use it for a pre-show special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4337901791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.3839489978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、それだとカメラマンの方がかなりの時間\n張り付くことになるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But if that’s the case‚ wouldn’t the cameraman\nbe stuck with us for quite a long time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7839486164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりそんな状況になったら\nレッスンや仕事に支障をきたすかもしれないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that happens suddenly‚\nit might interfere with our practice and work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3839577717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5839581531
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、このドキュメンタリー映像を撮ることが\n出演の条件なんです。うーん、困ったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But filming this documentary\nis a condition of our appearance. Hmm‚ this is a problem…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.466668101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4220750214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "他の出演者さん達も\nみんな密着取材を受けるのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other performers\nare all getting close-up coverage‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.22207464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。なんとかお願い出来ませんか？\n俺に出来ることならなんでもしますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Please‚ is there any way you could agree to this?\nI’ll do anything I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4333347677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.2768371624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_08_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……貴方も素直な割に、引かない人だものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… You’re naive‚ but you don’t know when to give up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2768371624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.4101694784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
