      "text": "そうよ。貴方が私に張り付きなさい\n貴方なら付き合いも長いし、みんな気にしないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. You’re going to be stuck with me.\nWe’ve known each other for a long time‚ so I’m sure everyone will be fine with it.",
